MYSTERIOUS GIRL: "Hello dearest climbers What better way to start your trial than beating up some fairy. The goal is simple collect at least 2 different orbs. But they are being heavily guarded so be careful :P"

This is **Floor 1: Hakurei Shrine**. 

To clear this floor and teleport out, the party must at least collect **2 Orbs** (one from each area). However, they aren't alone. **A Rival Party of 4 NPCs** (The "Moonlight Squad") is on the same floor, trying to collect the same orbs.

